TI  - SHock-INduced Endotheliopathy (SHINE): A mechanistic justification for viscoelastography-guided resuscitation of traumatic and non-traumatic shock
JO  - FRONTIERS IN PHYSIOLOGY
PY  - 2023
AU  - Bunch, CM
AU  - Chang, E
AU  - Moore, EE
AU  - Moore, HB
AU  - Kwaan, HC
